{
  "stem": "24259.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm told by the time that we were liberated, we were really just skin and bones and so forth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That would be a very special thing to eat, if there was any available.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And occasionally, my father would even go through the-- the food that they would give to the pigs, and that would be some leftover things, possibly spoiled things.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he would find something that he felt was edible, and he would bring it back into the hole, and we would use that to stay alive as food.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I really don't recall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you'll probably-- [INAUDIBLE] I am sure I probably urinated right there and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It would be absorbed into the ground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the sanitary conditions were almost nonexistent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We would have water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, they would leave water for the cows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So occasionally, my father would find a way to bring water down to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, it was probably very minimal, just enough to stay alive and comfortable.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Same way, right, just on occasion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At one point, I would-- I'm told I was going up to the attic of the barn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just as I was going up on a ladder, the door opened up to the barn and we were almost discovered.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And fortunately, that did not occur.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then as a result of that, my going up to the attic became more infrequent.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really don't know specifically.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think it was the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was probably perhaps other farmers or neighbors that came with the farmer, and they-- for whatever reason, they had to go into the barn and so forth.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
